This is a course project for the "Programming in C" course.

Instructions for the course can be found at:
http://www.cs.helsinki.fi/node/62063
http://www.cs.helsinki.fi/node/65829

Compilation:

$ make

Running tests:

$ make run_tests
$ make run_tests2

Running the main program:

$ ./wordcount inputfile outputfile
$ ./wordcount < inputfile > outputfile

